The paper proposes a method for deriving formal specifications of systems, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the concept of layered fault-tolerant specification, which involves the use of formal methods and logic (cs.PL, cs.LO). The paper also deals with the dependability of systems, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SY).
